title: #35 - That Episode Where We Read Your Closure Letters with Katie Morse
description:
You loved it! We loved it! So we’re doing it again!

This week on the podcast, Maria is reading your closure letters with her friend Katie Morse. Those words you wish you could say to someone but you know it’s better you don’t. But you still need to get the words and feelings out!

We happily read them and put them out in the universe for you!

Plus, Maria and Katie talk about how they became friends. Spoiler alert: It started when they realized that at one point they both were with the same guy!

To learn how Maria can help you find love in 2021, go to: https://linktr.ee/agapematch
